  "detailed_description": "This video demonstrates a comprehensive men's hair styling routine using various products and tools to achieve a slicked-back, well-groomed look. The process begins with wetting and rough shaping of the hair, followed by precise combing to create a distinct side part. A hairdryer and brush are utilized to set the foundational style. Subsequently, hair oil is applied for nourishment and shine, and styling cream is worked through the hair for hold and definition. The routine concludes with a final setting spray and detailed combing, showcasing the refined end result from multiple angles, emphasizing the transformation.",
